dc_title_s: Transportation, Planimetric Feature Areas: Prince George's County, Maryland, 2014
dc_description_s: This dataset contains roads, parking lots, runways and taxiways, driveways, railroad beds, and walkways/sidewalks within Prince George's County. Roads, parking lots, and railroad beds are attributed with surface type. Driveways, runways and taxiways, and walkways/sidewalks are attributed as either paved or unpaved. This data was captured for use in general mapping at a scale of 1:1200.
dc_creator_sm: The Maryland-National Capital Park & Planning Commission
